Checkerboard in the lab
23 mm squares
9x6 squares
rosrun camera_calibration cameracalibrator.py --size 9x6 --square 0.23 image:=/usb_cam/image_raw camera:=/usb_cam

To republish a video file:
roslaunch ros2opencv avi2ros.launch input:=/path/to/avi/file

New board:
6 cm squares
9x6 squares

rosrun camera_calibration cameracalibrator.py --size 10x7 --square 6 image:=/ardrone/front/image_raw camera:=/ardrone/front/
